  "metadata": {
    "modules": [
      {
        "name": "MarketplaceKit"
      }
    ],
    "role": "article",
    "roleHeading": "Article",
    "title": "Enabling alternative distribution app installation in a browser"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To enable the installation of an alternative distribution app from a webpage, your browser listens for installation requests from the website visitor’s interaction with the page and hands off the request to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". The installation request uses a specific URL scheme (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit/MarketplaceKitURIScheme",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") that the marketplace page assigns to a button. ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " handles the request by presenting the app install sheet, in which the person can confirm and install the alternative distribution app on their device.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "enabling-alternative-distribution-app-installation-in-a-browser-1.png",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " requires a one-to-one mapping between an alternative distribution app and the domain of the website that distributes it. When a page visitor taps a button to install the app, your browser app passes the origin of the site’s main frame to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", which confirms that the owner of the domain also owns the app.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The system requires that your browser app have a specific entitlement to call the ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " installation method. For more information and to request the entitlement, see ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.browser.app-installation",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Respond-to-app-installation-requests-using-BrowserEngineKit",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Respond to app installation requests using BrowserEngineKit",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Browsers that render using ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BrowserEngineKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " hand off app installation requests to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Your browser listens for invocations to a URL with the scheme ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "MarketplaceKit/MarketplaceKitURIScheme",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ":",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "marketplace-kit://install",
            "    ?alternativeDistributionPackage=<url>",
            "    &installVerificationToken=<install verification token>",
            "    &token=<authentication token>",
            "    &account=<user id>",
            "    &appShareURL=<URL>;"
          ],
          "syntax": null,
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The URL parameters are:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "header": "row",
          "rows": [
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "URL parameter",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Description",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "alternativeDistributionPackage",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The app to install in the form of an alternative distribution package.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "installVerificationToken",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A required JSON web signature (JWS).",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "token",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "An optional authentication token.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "account",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "An optional user ID for the page visitor.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "appShareURL",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "An optional URL to a product landing page for the app on the marketplace website.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "type": "table"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information about the parameters, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit/MarketplaceKitURIScheme",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To forward the navigation request to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", call the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit/AppLibrary/requestAppInstallationFromBrowser(for:referrer:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method to display the app install sheet and pass in the following parameters:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "header": "row",
          "rows": [
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "URL parameter",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Description",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "url",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The unparsed ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit/MarketplaceKitURIScheme",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " URL that triggers the installation request.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "referrer",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The origin of the main frame that contains the alternative marketplace installation URL.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "type": "table"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "To comply with operation system requirements, ignore the ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "marketplace-kit://",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " URL invocation if the navigation doesn’t result from a user interaction, such as tapping a button, or if the navigation results from a redirect.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "style": "important",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Respond-to-app-installation-requests-using-WebKit",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Respond to app installation requests using WebKit",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If your browser app uses ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/WebKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", modify your app’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/webkit/wknavigationdelegate/1455641-webview",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " navigation delegate method. When the system calls the delegate method with a URL matching the  ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "MarketplaceKitURIScheme",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " scheme, call the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "decisionHandler",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " with a value of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "WKNavigationActionPolicyAllow",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Don’t call the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit/AppLibrary/requestAppInstallationFromBrowser(for:referrer:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " method directly. WebKit handles the interaction with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ManagedAppDistribution/documentation/MarketplaceKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " after you call the navigation delegate’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "decisionHandler",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " with a value of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "WKNavigationActionPolicyAllow",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Safari is an example of a browser app that uses ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/WebKit",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". When a person taps on an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "MarketplaceKitURIScheme",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " URL, it calls Safari’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/webkit/wknavigationdelegate/1455641-webview",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " navigation delegate method with a URL matching the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "MarketplaceKitURIScheme",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Safari responds by calling ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "decisionHandler",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "WKNavigationActionPolicyAllow",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", which then causes WebKit to pass the URL to MarketplaceKit and display an install sheet.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Test-web-distribution-during-development",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Test web distribution during development",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In iOS or iPadOS 18.2 and later, development builds of browser apps with the default browser entitlement (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.web-browser",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") can test the installation of app marketplaces and other apps that distribute over the web. A development build signed with a development or Ad Hoc provisioning profile can run on Simulator and all supported physical devices (iPhone and iPad).",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
